<BR>
Warriors were designed to have the best ARMOR CLASS in the game. Thats right! So if you started out a warrior character so you could show off your incredible ability to do damage; then your screwed! Just look at all the wonderful items with AC that warriors, and warriors alone can have. It's very possible to have a warrior with an AC item equiped in every slot. Also In my opinion and experience, Warriors only get high damage weapons so they can aggrovate mobs so they can get the crap beat out of them!! Let's face it kiddies; We need Clerics to heal us, and warriors to AGGRO mobs, and keep them busy. We do this best when heavily protected; Not when doing the most damage.<BR>
<BR>
So all you warriors who think you should be doing more damage than any of the melee classes should just put those silly thoughts aside. If that were the case who the hell would play a monk or rouge? It's time to face the music fella's. We were meant to die!! First ones in, last ones out!! So get the best armor class possible so we can do our job the right way!!<BR>
